OL,3,CLottery winner spends prize on garden
OL,4,Cgolf course for people with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FA lottery winner has fulfilled his
OL,8,Fdream of creating a crazy golf course
OL,9,Fin his back garden, to help support
OL,10,Fpeople with disabilities and complex
OL,11,Fneeds.
OL,13,FDavid Lawrence, 68, from Leatherhead
OL,14,Fin Surrey won #1 million on the
OL,15,FNational Lottery last year. But for
OL,16,Fover 30 years before that, he had been
OL,17,Fan avid fundraiser.
