OL,3,CLottery winner spends prize on garden
OL,4,Cgolf course for people with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FAfter winning his prize, he made it
OL,8,Fhis mission to create a golf course,
OL,9,Fwhich he named Dave's Putting
OL,10,FChallenge, to host a community event
OL,11,Ffor those with complex needs.
OL,13,FMr Lawrence has invited multiple local
OL,14,Fdisability organisations to the
OL,15,Fcourse, aptly named Dave's Putting
OL,16,FChallenge. He hopes that his putting
OL,17,Fcourse will inspire people living with
OL,18,Fdisabilities to play golf, drawing on
OL,19,Fhis experience working as a day
OL,20,Fservice officer at Surrey County
OL,21,FCouncil.
