OL,3,CLottery winner spends prize on garden
OL,4,Cgolf course for people with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,F"Many years ago I provided support
OL,8,Fservices for a young man who had
OL,9,Flearning difficulties. He was always
OL,10,Fvery introverted except for the
OL,11,Foccasions we visited a local couple
OL,12,Fwho had a small putting green in their
OL,13,Fgarden and he would really come out of
OL,14,Fhis shell," he said.
