OL,7,F"That was probably 20 years ago but I
OL,8,Fstill remember the look of sheer joy
OL,9,Fon his face and if Dave's Putting
OL,10,FChallenge can help and inspire
OL,11,Fchildren and adults with learning
OL,12,Fdifficulties and social care needs in
OL,13,Fthe same way, that's like winning the
OL,14,FNational Lottery every time."
