OL,7,FThe design of the course partly draws
OL,8,Finspiration from Mr Lawrence's
OL,9,Ffundraising. He has fundraised for
OL,10,Fnational charities, including the
OL,11,FBBC's Children In Need, for more than
OL,12,F35 years.
