OL,3,CLottery winner spends prize on garden
OL,4,Cgolf course for people with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FThe course has three holes, each with
OL,8,Fa different theme, including Pudsey
OL,9,FBear as a nod to Children in Need, a
OL,10,Fjungle-themed putting hole featuring
OL,11,Fhis granddaughter's favourite animals,
OL,12,Fand an area known as the "Boccia
OL,13,FStadium" to celebrate the sport of
OL,14,Fboccia, a ball game introduced into
OL,15,Fthe Paralympic Games in 1984 and which
OL,16,Fdoes not have an Olympic equivalent.
OL,18,FDespite his lottery win, Mr Lawrence
OL,19,Fsaid he has no plan to slow his
OL,20,Ffundraising efforts.
