OL,3,CLottery winner spends prize on garden
OL,4,Cgolf course for people with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,F"People thought I might take it easier
OL,8,Ffollowing the win but I am a true
OL,9,Fbeliever that it really is better to
OL,10,Fgive than to receive and my
OL,11,Ffundraising and community work gives
OL,12,Fme so much joy, why would I stop?"
OL,14,FHe has run marathons and hosted
OL,15,Fseveral other events to support
OL,16,FChildren In Need, but hopes to
OL,17,Fcontinue raising money for the charity
OL,18,Ffrom his back garden.
