OL,7,F"While the crazy golf course is a
OL,8,Flittle easier to complete than a
OL,9,Fmarathon, I hope it will be just as
OL,10,Frewarding on the occasions we open up
OL,11,Ffor Children In Need fundraising," he
OL,12,Fsaid
OL,14,FIn November, the National Lottery will
OL,15,Fmark 30 years since its creation.
